Handa na silang lumipat.

00:26:34.220 --> 00:26:36.460
Nakita mo na kung gaano kalaki ang Hidden Soldier Alley.

00:26:36.830 --> 00:26:37.730
Isang libong lalaki

00:26:38.330 --> 00:26:40.190
hindi sapat para matalo.

00:26:47.240 --> 00:26:49.500
Taglay ang badge na ito, maaari kang makapasok sa palasyo,

00:26:49.640 --> 00:26:50.700
at makita ang Kanyang Kamahalan.

00:26:51.270 --> 00:26:53.390
Pakilosin ang mga Imperial at Kanang Kabalyeriya

00:26:53.680 --> 00:26:54.330
at

00:26:54.800 --> 00:26:57.150
palibutan nang lubusan ang Hidden Soldier Alley.

00:26:57.830 --> 00:27:00.500
Gusto ko sina Xie Huai'an at Han Ziling

00:27:01.310 --> 00:27:02.330
nahuli nang buhay.

00:27:06.240 --> 00:27:07.370
Alam ko ang mga panlilinlang ni Huai'an

00:27:07.960 --> 00:27:09.130
