00:32:18.550 --> 00:32:19.610
Dahil alam mo

00:32:20.790 --> 00:32:21.500
may mga bagay

00:32:21.550 --> 00:32:22.850
Si Gu Yu lang ang makakapag-ayos.

00:32:23.160 --> 00:32:23.780
Tama?

