00:32:41.520 --> 00:32:42.540
Kailangan mong manatiling buhay.

00:32:44.350 --> 00:32:46.260
Ikaw lang ang makakapagpabagsak sa Huben.

00:32:48.300 --> 00:32:49.900
Kung talagang nakakaramdam ka ng pagkakasala,

00:32:50.550 --> 00:32:51.930
kung gayon, dalhin mo ang aking kamatayan

00:32:51.930 --> 00:32:53.610
at patayin si Yan Fengshan.

00:32:56.160 --> 00:32:58.330
Kapag sa wakas ay nawasak mo na ang Huben,

00:32:59.480 --> 00:33:00.740
